node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Evan Tang in Ginza Tendon Itsuki. Image may contain: food

node.text:
Dabao-ed this tasty Tempura Set ($15.90++) from Tendon Ginza Itsuki for lunch the other day!

I was impressed by the high quality packaging!

The tempura was tasty, though the batter would probably have been more crispy if eaten fresh in the shop.

Overall this was still quite a satisfying meal!

Hope everyone had a good Sunday, and Happy Mother’s Day to all you wonderful moms out there 😊❤️
Happy mother's day to all the mummies out there ❤️🌹
I miss tendon, the one at Suntec 😍😢
The food seems nice and I love the packaging as well! 😍 I am constantly looking for food that offers nice packaging as well. This one is worth considering! 👍👍
@3wheelingtots have a great week too Lawrence 😊
Am impressed by japanese’s restaurant’s way of packaging too! Have a great week!
